cast.overview: Predestination chronicles the life of a Temporal Agent sent on an intricate series of time-travel journeys designed to prevent future killers from committing their crimes. Now, on his final assignment, the Agent must stop the one criminal that has eluded him throughout time and prevent a devastating attack in which thousands of lives will be lost.
cast.title: Predestination

cast.overview: In 1933 New York, an overly ambitious movie producer coerces his cast and hired ship crew to travel to mysterious Skull Island, where they encounter Kong, a giant ape who is immediately smitten with the leading lady.
cast.title: King Kong

details.biography: James Joseph "Jim" Knobeloch is an American actor best known for his role as Jake Slicker on Dr. Quinn, Medicine Woman. He was formerly married to Beth Sullivan,an American film and television writer and producer, best known as the creator of the long-running CBS series Dr. Quinn, Medicine Woman.. They have two children, Tess and Jack, who live in northern California with their mother.
details.name: Jim Knobeloch
